      "parameters": {
        "width": 480,
        "height": 576,
        "content": "## Gmail Review Sentiment Router to Slack\n\n### How it works\n\n1. Gmail trigger receives email reviews.\n2. Checks are performed to ensure the review is new and not a duplicate.\n3. OpenAI classifies the sentiment of the new review.\n4. Reviews are routed based on their sentiment.\n5. Alerts are sent to Slack or logged in Google Sheets accordingly.\n\n### Setup steps\n\n- [ ] Ensure Gmail API is configured and connected.\n- [ ] Verify OpenAI API key is set up.\n- [ ] Connect Slack API with the necessary webhook.\n- [ ] Set up Google Sheets API access for reading and logging data.\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
